*/
"LewisRosalieRamp":"Rosalie was always a bit of a strange child. Quiet. Except when around her family and... never mind.",
"LewisRosalieArrivalCT1": "It's good to see folks come back to their roots.$h #$b# As they say, there's no place like home!$h",
"LewisRosalieArrivalCT2": "Well, it seems Rosalie has grown up to become a beautiful young lady!$h #$b# It's really too bad she gained all that weight though.$h",
"Lewis.RosalieGeorgeWCCT": "I understand where George is coming from. But that doesn't make what happened between him and Rosalie right.",
"Lewis.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "It's unfortunate that Rosalie ended up marrying the wrong man. #$b# The process in the city isn't as easy as it is here in Pelican Town.",


/*
Linus
*/
"LinusRosalieArrivalCT": "Rosalie gave me some interesting food last night that was off menu.$h #$e# She's also a wonderful baker, offered to make me a birthday cake!$h",
"LinusRosalieArrivalCT2": "I heard Rosalie singing as she cleaned the saloon last night. #$b# She sang a song my grandmother used to sing as a child... #$b# I... forgot about it until I heard it again...$2",

"Linus.RosalieGeorgeWCCT": "I know that my lifestyle isn't for everyone. #$b# I'm very lucky to be physically able to live the life I choose.",

/*
Marnie
*/    //In SHANE's file//


/*
