*/
"MaruRosalieArrivalCT1": "I had no idea that Gus' niece was also a person of colour! #$b# It's nice to have something in common with her already!$h",
"MaruRosalieArrivalCT2": "Harvey's been... weirdly distracted lately...$s #$e$It's like he's trying to remember something but doesn't know what...$s", 

"Maru.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "I knew there was something going on with Rosalie, but she never let on what it was.$s #$b# I was surprised Harvey knew. I guess that explains why she was always here. They shared a secret.$s #$e# I hope she knows that we're behind her, and she has our support. #$e# My mom can sometimes mean well, but say the wrong thing... I'm sure Rose knows that though.",

"Maru.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT1": "Either Harvey misses Rosalie dropping off coffee, or the company with it.$s",
"Maru.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT2": "I've caught Harvey looking toward the saloon when he thinks no one's looking.$2",
"Maru.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT3": "The first time Rosalie came into the clinic, I had to pick up her jaw off the floor when she saw Dr Harvey.$1 #$b# She's still friendly with him, but less interested in his interests.$2 #$b# I think he misses that...$2",
"Maru.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT4": "Rosalie says that she and Shane are just friends, but looking at the, I don't know if either of them are getting the memo.",


/*
