"Pam.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "Rosalie is getting a divorce, huh? #$b# Good for her! Marriage isn't for everyone, and it's better she's out now while she's young!$h #$e# She's lucky she doesn't have kids though. That always makes it tough...$s",

/*
Penny*/
"PennyRosalieArrivalCT": "Jas has been a bit upset lately... I hope things are okay at home.$s",
"PennyRosalieArrivalCTShaneSober": "Jas has been a bit upset lately...$s #$b# I hoped things would be better since Shane cut down on his drinking...$s",

"Penny.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "I'm sure Rosalie had a good reason not to stay married. Life's too short to be with someone who makes you unhappy. #$e# I do miss my dad sometimes, but my parents were miserable together...$s",

"Penny.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT": "Jas has been so happy since Rosalie and Shane have been spending time together.",

