*/

"PierreRosalieRamp": "Ah, a new customer to rip off! #$b# I hope she doesn't expect me to give her a discount just because she's Gus' niece!$h #$b# Did I say that outloud?$s",
"PierreRosalieArrivalCT": "I hope Rosalie grew up to be like her mother. #$b# And by that I mean she doesn't complain about my prices!$h #$b# Her father on the other hand...$3",
